snippet: Defending champion Andy Murray posted another straight-set victory to reach the fourth round at Wimbledon on Friday, beating Roberto Bautista Agut 6-2, 6-3, 6-2....
lead_paragraph: Defending champion Andy Murray posted another straight-set victory to reach the fourth round at Wimbledon on Friday, beating Roberto Bautista Agut 6-2, 6-3, 6-2.
